The given Perl script example misses the new line character. I tried the given example and the request hangs indefinitely. If the new line is added, the request is performed gracefully. The correct Perl script is as follows:

#!/usr/bin/perl
$| = 1;
while (<STDIN>) {
    # ...put here any transformations or lookups...
    print $_ . $/;
}

I hope this helps someone.
